{"tid":2110320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國安會指川普並未排除對中國官員進一步制裁","createTime":"2020-07-15T23:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T04:12:30.000Z","uid":28765,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c6a54d7b8668d0991d42dfbef634667fed91e920","tid":2110320,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T23:44:55.000Z","msg":"「香港自治法」允許川普對涉及港版國安法的中國官員實施制裁和簽證限制。《彭博》報導指出，白宮提出的制裁名單包含中國副總理韓正、香港特首林鄭月娥等，但川普目前不願對中國官員施加額外制裁，原因是不希望華盛頓和北京的緊張關係進一步升高。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，美國安會發言人John Ullyot駁斥，稱川普上週已對侵犯新疆維族人權的中國官員實施制裁，「川普沒有任何理由把制裁中國官員的選項拿到檯面下，諸如此類的匿名消息來源錯得離譜。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3229977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3229977&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n36npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=056e83fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3229977&h=18ec81fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3229977</a>"},{"pid":"136dcc216b73faca1ae5feb79e687966d6af49cf","tid":2110320,"uid":143343,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T23:46:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb13a509c92786ae39b4df3f94e32282cbad28f1","tid":2110320,"uid":143343,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T23:47:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dabf95da8cd897c56c676a24c5a8bce1fe53a4a","tid":2110320,"uid":58841,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T23:54:25.000Z","msg":"真心彭博啲料信唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82974bc6be89bde72d172dc7f53e1534585ce70a","tid":2110320,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T23:56:04.000Z","msg":"愛侵力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2433e935496201128a7d1ef5cf5de728692e223d","tid":2110320,"uid":4783,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"q